subtitles.original:
Departures 〜あなたにおくるアイの歌〜
Lyrics, Music: ryo
subtitles.english:
Departures ~A Song of Love for You~
Lyrics, Music: ryo

subtitles.original: もうあなたから愛されることも
subtitles.english: Being loved by you no longer...

subtitles.original: 必要とされることもない
subtitles.english: ...nor being needed by you exists anymore.

subtitles.original: そして私はこうして一人ぼっちで
subtitles.english: And so, I am here all alone like this.

subtitles.original: あの時あなたは何て言ったの?
subtitles.english: What did you say back then?

subtitles.original: 届かない言葉は宙を舞う
subtitles.english: The words that cannot reach dance in the air.

subtitles.original: わかってるのに今日もしてしまう
subtitles.english: Even though I know, I do it again today.

subtitles.original: 叶わぬ願いごとを
subtitles.english: Making a wish that won't come true.

subtitles.original: 離さないで ぎゅっと 手を握ってて
subtitles.english: Don't let go, hold my hand tightly.

subtitles.original: あなたと二人 続くと言って
subtitles.english: Tell me that the two of us will continue.

subtitles.original: 繋いだその手は温かくて
subtitles.english: The hand I held was so warm...

subtitles.original: 優しかった
subtitles.english: ...it was so kind.

subtitles.original: あなたはいつもそうやって私を
subtitles.english: You always do that to me...

subtitles.original: 怒らせて最後には泣かすんだ
subtitles.english: ...making me angry and making me cry in the end.

subtitles.original: だけど後になって「ごめんね」と言う
subtitles.english: But then later you would say "I'm sorry".

subtitles.original: その顔 好きだった
subtitles.english: I loved that face of yours.

subtitles.original: 離さないで ぎゅっと 思い切り
subtitles.english: Don't let go, hold me tight with all your might.

subtitles.original: あなたの腕の中にいたい
subtitles.english: I want to be in your arms.

subtitles.original: 二人で...
subtitles.english: Together we...
